{
  "stem": "12289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was bribed in a way that I had promised him that, if he cooperates, I will see to it that he, after the war, will-- will become a resident of Switzerland or any country where-- when he want to leave this, which I-- which I did then, later on.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He survived the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- I don't think that they ever suspected that he was on our side and all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Batis Falvi was his name, Batis Falvi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a-- a police officer and was standing there, in uniform, with all of the medals on-- on-- on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A very impressive person, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Germans didn't suspect, other than, now, he's going to take them, perhaps to a German-- to an Hungarian prison.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was the game we were playing, you know, with him, with his help.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what was happening physically with all these people that you saved?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That particular day, these people, did they went to the safe house?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh yes, we took them to the safe houses.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He more or less marched with them to there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and there were Germans, who thought, oh, now, they're going-- he going to take them to prison.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
